  "description": [
    "MILLVILLE Millie C Banks Phone Dickerson Ml The WSCS met last Tuesday evening with Mrs John Baker in Ocean View Because of the holi d a y s few members attended Members enjoyed an evening of fellowship Mr and Mrs Edward Short were holiday guests last Tuesday of Mr and Mrs Courtney Evans in Salisbury Mr and Mrs Thomas Hickman re turned home on Monday after spending the holidays in Florida Mr and Mrs Wallace Melaon and children spent last week visit ing relatives in Albany NY Mr and Mrs Lewis Duncan called on Mr and Mrs Ruley Banks last Thursday night The granddaughter Mrs Alma Reed and children of Chincotea gue Va visited Mrs Arlanta Sim pler during Christmas week Mr and Mrs Garrison Long and Linwood Hall of Baltimore spent the holidays with their parents Mr and Mrs Israel Townsend West Set man a patient in the Beebe Hospital is not too well at this time We wish West an early recovery Mr and Mrs Linwood Town serui entertained their parents Mr and Mrs Elisha Quillen to dinner last Wednesday Mrs Flossie Cobb was the guest at dinner with Mr and Mrs James Savage in South Bethany Beach"
